Program: Discovery
Title: Montserrat's volcano
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrx44
Last Broadcast Date: 30 April 1998
The Montserrat volcano eruption. The Caribbean island has been affected by the current wave of erruptions since 1995 but the volcano is showing signs of slowing down. Also in the programm, new treatments for cancer and how being a big baby can affect your health later in life. Presenter: Dee Palmer.